Default:
- Function keys are aliases/macros, double tap for functions
- Capslock -> Esc
- Double arrow for PgUp, PgDn, Home and End

Utility:
- Layer navigation - Function Row
- Reboot/flash - PrtSc
- Sleep - Pause
- Lock - ScrLk
- Record macro - Grave
- Custom macros - Number Row
- NKRO/6KRO - Ins/Del
- Brightness controls - Home/End
- Volume controls - PgUp/PgDn
- Media controls - pause/play/next/prev/volume/mute - green

Num pad and navigation:
- RGB:
+  Numpad on left hand is __
+  Vim navigation on right is __


Media:
- Youtube - red
- Spotify/generic - green
